'''SendSpace''' (typeset as '''''send''space''') is a [[File hosting service|file hosting]] [[website]]. It offers temporary file hosting to enable users to send and receive large files that are too big for email attachments. Users can upload and download files up to 500MB each for free (up to 10GB files can be uploaded with the paid service), and have the ability to manage and edit their uploads.
As of June 2009, it has an [[Alexa internet|Alexa ranking]] of 328.<ref>[http://www.alexa.com/data/details/traffic_details/sendspace.com]</ref>
== SendSpace Wizard == SendSpace Wizard is a [[software]] that allows users to upload files from the desktop, without the need of a web interface. It is available for [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]], [[Mac OS]] and [[Linux]].
